scene.message:
Nanjo: That's about it.{wait_fr:64}{nl}
By the way, it seems{nl}
you're the real Kido.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Heh-heh.{nl}
Clean out your ears{nl}
and listen up.{waitkey}This is a school we know,{nl}
and yet it isn't!{waitkey}{clearbox}It's a school in another{nl}
world! Surprised, huh!{nl}
Dang it!{wait_fr:60} Boo-hoo...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I'm the one with{nl}
questions~ This being another{nl}
world, can you believe it?{waitkey}I just don't get it~{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Kandori flung us into{nl}
a nearly identical world.{nl}
You're the same, aren't you?{waitkey}{clearbox}The boy sent into the rift{nl}
between dimensions that{nl}
Kandori and that scientist{nl}
spoke of - that's you.{wait_fr:88} No?{waitkey}{clearbox}Why are you, who were sent{nl}
into the rift, here unharmed?{nl}
Why do you pursue Kandori?{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{wait_fr:94}I was drifting{nl}
through a void when a kid{nl}
in white clothes appeared...{waitkey}{clearbox}Next thing I knew,{nl}
I was here. That's all...{nl}
I owe you no more than that.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Don't be so prickly.{nl}
We're gonna pound Kandori{nl}
and find a way home.{waitkey}{clearbox}You come too.{nl}
Your mom's gotta be{nl}
worried about you.{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: Shut up!{nl}
I've no intention of{nl}
running with you lot!{waitkey}I do as I please.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: What's that?!{nl}
I show some concern and{nl}
you get all cocky!{waitkey}{clearbox}Fine, do what you want!{nl}
Drop dead in a ditch for{nl}
all I care! You jerk!{waitkey}{clearbox}{wait_fr:60}What's with that guy...{nl}
Just mention his mom and{nl}
his whole face changes...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Stop it, Inaba.{nl}
Nothing you say will help.{nl}
He's got those kind of eyes...{waitkey}{clearbox}Kandori must have hurt{nl}
something precious to him,{nl}
just like he did to us...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Quit prying, quit it!{nl}
Everybody's got things they{nl}
don't want touched, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Are you running a{nl}
fever, Uesugi? That's a{nl}
sensible thing for you to say.{waitkey}You look like you{nl}
understand how he feels.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Wh-what?{nl}
A guy as straightforward as{nl}
me is a rare thing, y'know?{waitkey}I could get declared a{nl}
national treasure any day now!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: A fool as ever...{nl}
Now then, {ctl0f:1},{nl}
shall we get going?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: What's that, Nanjo!{nl}
Even as a national treasure,{nl}
I won't speak to you!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ehh~ That guy's got{nl}
something like that?{nl}
Isn't he just antisocial~?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: He's... Kido, was it?{nl}
I'm sure even Kido has{nl}
things that matter to him.{waitkey}Friends... dreams for{nl}
the future, and so on.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ...Dreams for the{nl}
future?{wait_fr:80} As long as now{nl}
is good, who cares.{nl}
How dumb...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: How should I even{nl}
explain that this isn't{nl}
your world...{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: What?{nl}
So that bastard's here too?{wait_fr:108}{nl}
Fine then...{waitkey}I'll go along with you lot.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Then it's settled!{nl}
I'm Maki Sonomura!{nl}
Nice to meet you, Kido!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: What?{nl}
Is there something{nl}
on my face?{wait_fr:108} Ah!{waitkey}{clearbox}You were so taken with{nl}
how cute I am that you{nl}
couldn't look away, right?{nl}
Yeah, I get it, I get it.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: C-come on,{nl}
we can't dawdle forever.{nl}
Let's hurry up and go!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Kido... you said a{nl}
'child in white' saved you,{nl}
right? Could it be...{waitkey}{clearbox}maybe it was little Mai...{nl}
I've seen her a few times.{nl}
A very mysterious girl...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: C'mon, c'mon, let's go!{nl}
Huh? 'What are you{nl}
so worked up about'?{waitkey}Shut up!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Leave him be.{nl}
He's after the same man.{nl}
We'll surely meet again.{waitkey}{clearbox}As long as he doesn't{nl}
get in our way,{nl}
that's fine.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Why Kido pursues{nl}
Kandori? We'll learn{nl}
in time, I suppose.{waitkey}For now, it's enough{nl}
that he's of use to us.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Something precious...{nl}
Someone precious...{nl}
{ctl07:1}, you...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I see...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
For me...{wait_fr:60} I'm sorry{nl}
for asking something{nl}
so strange...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I see...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
Then you're the same{nl}
as me...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Y'know, it's not{nl}
nice to go prying into{nl}
what people keep hidden.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: See? See?{nl}
Knew it, right?{nl}
That's just how people are!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Yeah, right~?{nl}
Is your bond with me{nl}
really this skin-deep?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: No point thinking{nl}
about the future, right?{nl}
You think so too, {ctl0f:1}?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: ...{wait_fr:60}What the heck!{nl}
Dummy dummy dummy dummy{nl}
dummy dummy dummy!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: That Sonomura girl...{nl}
I don't feel like it's{nl}
our first meeting...{waitkey}What is she...?{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Reiji Kido.{nl}
A student who transferred{nl}
in half a year ago. Quiet,{nl}
always acts alone.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}
